Package: pantheon-mail
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Email client
 Mail is an email client built for elementary's Pantheon desktop environment. It
 allows you to read and send email with a simple, modern interface.
 .
 Visit http://elementary.io to read about the current state of
 Mail's development.

